* Map
    - next_scene
    - opening_scene
* Engine
    - play
* Scene
    - enter
    * Death
    * Central Corridor
    * Laser Weapon Armory
    * The Bridge
    * Escape Pod
    
Stanley Parable

Central Corridor -> Laser Weapon Armory -> The Bridge -> Escape Pod
        |                   |                   |           |
        Death                                   Death       Death
        
Map object has the structure for the scenes. It the information about the opening
scene and about which scene to call next_scene

Scene object contains the information about the scenes. It has the text and the 
choices that are used in a scene. It gives the result of a choice to Engine? or Map?
